Anamarie Fleischman, a U.S. citizen from Roanoke, Ind., started her 50-year prison sentence April 15, for making and distributing child sex abuse material.

🔎Fleischman’s conviction was made possible because of an ICE @HSI_HQ -led probe, in cooperation with the Indiana State Police and the Regional Internet Crimes Against Children Task Force.

@HSIChicago

